	[dropoff_datetime] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[passenger_count] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[trip_time_in_secs] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[trip_distance] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[pickup_longitude] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[pickup_latitude] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
	[dropoff_longitude] [nvarchar](max)  NULL,
